{"tid":1098404,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"政府工老屎忽","createTime":"2019-04-09T04:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T04:56:38.000Z","uid":112716,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5cc99248e73dee04812396613295865a4341d5c1","tid":1098404,"uid":112716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T04:46:38.000Z","msg":"我早排爺爺過咗身，嫲嫲又入院，個人唔係咁開心，成個星期都喺苦瓜乾咁嘅樣。<br />\n<br />\n有個老屎忽問我做咩最近成日補鐘走，我照答佢。<br />\n<br />\n跟住最近發現個老屎忽個樣好似唔妥我，我喺人地口中聽到原來係因為佢覺得我唔開心所以令到佢好唔開心，跟住唔妥我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做乜勁 姐喺我唔開心都要氹佢開心？"},{"pid":"0de2f5a327615003210e70a5008fe57f75f0519a","tid":1098404,"uid":161190,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:12:14.000Z","msg":"唔氹我呢d老屎忽唔通請你返嚟托柒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73830d006f155b0adb95fabbe0cb1dec1696b23e","tid":1098404,"uid":54502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:18:01.000Z","msg":"過左3年未先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d0b46a66aacca595b649037e5a5d837f954174e","tid":1098404,"uid":63864,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:25:03.000Z","msg":"政府d 老屎忽要屌佢一獲先得嫁，<br />\n果陣個老屎忽，話我唔做野之類<br />\n我立即大聲話，你日日上網仲好意思出聲？ 之後開始佢就避左我<br />\n呢d仆街真係欺善怕惡，之後其他同事講返原來都唔鐘意佢"},{"pid":"add764ebbf3812f93bf3071c8083d747ec33ff24","tid":1098404,"uid":112716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"73830d006f155b0adb95fabbe0cb1dec1696b23e","tid":1098404,"uid":54502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:18:01.000Z","msg":"過左3年未先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T06:11:59.000Z","msg":"一年都未過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a3baadd8d9c9c0d38c8f53afa87a8da9d659db","tid":1098404,"uid":92000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"add764ebbf3812f93bf3071c8083d74